## 13. Company-Specific References (optional)

For deeper customization, add additional .md files to this `company/` directory:

- **Founder frame** — how the founder's background changes the sale (see `references/founder-frame.md.template`)
- **Buyer psychology** — deep dive on how your specific buyers think and buy (see `references/buyer-psychology.md.template`)
- **Offer psychology** — how your free offer works as a sales tool (see `references/offer-psychology.md.template`)
- **Regional playbooks** — state/region-specific knowledge for your industry
- **Customer stories** — specific wins you can reference in outreach
